    "body": "Very likely to never be, at least not by this codebase. The underlying architecture is highly tuned around a multithreaded network polling system in C++, which makes supporting bare metal MCUs close to impossible. The blog post refers to devices like the raspberry pi. Please note that the post and documentation only talks about CPU. What you're referring to are MCUs. "
